# Equity Reserves Asset Revaluation Reserve Relating To Non Current Assets Or Disposal Groups Held For Sale Amount

## identifier
de1540

## type
float

## definition
Report the value as at the relevant date of the balance of the Asset Revaluation Reserve relating to the revaluation of non-current assets or disposal groups held for sale, determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Equity.Reserves.AssetRevaluationReserveRelatingToNonCurrentAssetsOrDisposalGroupsHeldForSale.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo2.02.00
- period=instant
